Reading The Four Agreements
Agreement
Resonance
- First attempt | 2 | Too familiar | Felt like spiritual advice in new packaging
- Second attempt | 2 | Same wall | Same stopping point as before
- Third attempt | 5 | Finally landed | Context changed everything this time
- After finishing | 4 | Ongoing practice | Simple ideas that require daily effort

:QUOTE [subtitle:Don Miguel Ruiz, quotetype:PLAIN]
Be impeccable with your word. Speak with integrity. Say only what you mean.

:TASK [status:in_progress]
